
================================================================================
CAMPUS HUB - COMPREHENSIVE PROJECT PROMPT
================================================================================

PROJECT OVERVIEW:
================================================================================

You are tasked with building "CAMPUS HUB" - a comprehensive College Campus 
Management Website designed to become an ESSENTIAL DIGITAL PLATFORM for college 
students to manage all aspects of their academic and campus life in one place.

This website will serve as a complete student portal that integrates all critical 
college services, resources, and information into a single, easy-to-use platform.

================================================================================
CORE PURPOSE & IMPORTANCE:
================================================================================

Campus Hub will be an ESSENTIAL PART of every college student's academic life 
because it will:

1. CENTRALIZE STUDENT INFORMATION
   - Maintain comprehensive student portal with verified credentials
   - Store personal details, contact information, and verification documents
   - Provide secure account management with profile customization
   - Enable students to access and update their own information

2. PROVIDE ACADEMIC RESOURCES & SCHEDULES
   - Provide easy access to lecture schedules and timetables
   - Display daily event updates and campus announcements
   - Organize and display all classroom notes shared by teachers
   - Make learning materials easily discoverable and accessible
   - Allow students to download PDFs, documents, and study materials

3. STREAMLINE COLLEGE COMMUNICATIONS
   - Display official notice board with college announcements
   - Share daily updates and important deadlines
   - Send notifications for events, notices, and academic updates
   - Keep students informed about college activities and requirements

4. MANAGE LIBRARY SERVICES
   - Provide library portal to browse and search book catalog
   - Maintain detailed borrowing history for each student
   - Track borrowed books, due dates, and return status
   - Enable easy lookup of book availability

5. HANDLE FINANCIAL & EXAM MANAGEMENT
   - Provide exam fee portal for viewing and paying exam fees
   - Display all exam results and grades in one place
   - Provide comprehensive progress tracking dashboard
   - Show academic performance metrics (CGPA, semester progress, etc.)
   - Track and display student academic achievements

6. ADDITIONAL CONVENIENCE FEATURES
   - Maintain contact directory of faculty and staff
   - Allow downloading of certificates and verification documents
   - Send real-time notifications for important updates
   - Provide settings and preferences management

